Keep the following things in mind when administering DCE accounts:
.ML
.LI
If you share files with other systems that do not use the registry, be sure
that names, UNIX IDs, and account information are consistent between the
registry and the foreign password and group files.  Use \*Lpasswd_import\*O
to identify and resolve any conflicts that exist.
