Ticket expiration date, password life span, password format, and password
expiration date are examples of registry policies that you can set.
If both an organizational policy and a registry policy exist
for password format, for example, the more restrictive policy applies.
.P
You can establish overrides to the information contained in the
registry.
Override information is stored in the \*Lpasswd_override\*O and
