.H 3 "Monitoring DFS Servers and Clients"
.iX "DFS" "monitoring"
.P
You can monitor DFS in the following ways:
.ML
.LI
Use the BOS server to continually monitor DFS server processes.  You define
which processes the BOS server monitors, and you control server process status
by issuing \*Lbos\*O commands to perform routine maintenance or to correct
errors in addition to those the BOS server handles. You can also use \*Lbos\*O
commands to restart DFS weekly.
See 
...\" Chapter 55
...\" \*VModule 6\*O "Monitoring and Controlling Server Processes"
the \*(Ad
for details about the BOS server and how to use \*Lbos\*O commands.
.LI
