.iX "scout"
Use the \*Lscout\*O program to monitor the File Exporter, which runs on File
server machines.  The File Exporter makes DFS files available to client
machines.  The \*Lscout\*O program
collects and displays information about the machines you
select to monitor.  It displays information such as disk usage and the
number of connections a machine has.
...\" For more information about Scout's features and example screens, see 
...\" Chapter 61.
...\" \*VModule 6\*O entitled "Monitoring File Exporters with Scout."
