.H 2 "Shutting Down DCE"
.P
When you wish to shut down the DCE processes, you can use the
\*Ldce_config\*O script (option 4 in the Main Menu), which calls the
\*Ldce_shutdown\*O script, or you can run the \*Ldce_shutdown\*O script
directly.  To run the \*Ldce_shutdown\*O script, enter the
following command:
.iS
sh /etc/dce_shutdown
.iE
